item.title: Travis Flock
item.description: Travis graduated with his Masters degree in June 2019. The title of his thesis is Density-Mediated Interactions are Stronger but More Variable Than Trait-Mediated Interactions Within Predator-Prey Systems. After graduation, Travis was hired by the Indiana Department of Environmental Management as an environmental manager in the Office of Air Quality.
